              div(class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0")
              span(class="text-sm text-white/90 flex-1 min-w-0 truncate") Database SQLite
              span(class="ml-auto inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/30") Online
            // Web server status
